    CONCLUSION: THE FUTURE OF RADIANT COHERENCE
    The Singing Machine is not merely a cooling solution; it is a stability protocol. By ensuring that every photon "sings" at the correct phase, we enable the first generation of truly scalable, high-precision photonic AI processors. The machine doesn't just calculate; it resonates with the data it processes.

